<emph>
P0560: System Voltage
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Main power supply voltage is lower than 2.54 V for 10 sec.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type A and C: 3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type B: 2 D/C detection logic)
