<ptxt>
<emph>
P0563: System Voltage High
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Main power supply circuit voltage is higher than 16.5 V for 10 sec. with engine running.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type A and C: 3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type B: 2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
